_sText:
This map was made 11-120605 by ogsh and Jacc0s.

The part where the Ts spawn is made by ogsh.
The part where the CTS spawn is made by Jacc0s.

Map info:

If you get into a little room with AUGs, you need to jump to get out.

Ts: Go through the teleport that is behind the car and plant bomb.
CTs: Prevent the bomb to explode.

There is also lots of secrets :O
